method.text:
Sets the text/HTML for the control to be displayed
on-screen; returns reference to self to facilitate method
chaining;

destroy's the on-screen VIEW for the HW container AND
removes any reference to the instance from the hash;
Destroy() affects the MODEL and the VIEW

Sets the overflow property for CONTENTS of the HW container;
it is assumed that anytime a perfect fit cannot occur that
the content will have its overflow property set to 'auto'
unless specified otherwise returns reference to self to
facilitate method chaining;
